    "headline": "Molson Coors Beverage Company Announces Regular Quarterly Dividend",
    "summary": "GOLDEN, Colo. & MONTREAL, May 07, 2026--The Board of Directors of Molson Coors Beverage Company (NYSE: TAP, TAP.A) today declared a regular quarterly dividend on its Class A and Class B common stock of US$0.48 per share, payable June 12, 2026, to stockholders of record on May 29, 2026. The quarterly dividend is payable to holders of Class A and Class B common stock of Molson Coors Beverage Company.",
